version_description: First chord tab of this version.
This is the "Before the Flood" Tour '74 version.  Nothing like the original.
Because there is allways missing the third vers of the song.
Live with Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers / Bob Dylan adds a verse to the song / He also changes the chorus and adds a second chorus / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pJVtHBHcuV0.
MTV Unplugged / with extra verse and altered lyrics in the chorus / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJpB_AEZf6U.
Easy to play, and good for most voices. It's not the original key of A, but this is better for a novice.
Complete with Intro and Coda / thoroughly ear-transcribed / intermediate with transitional chords (sus4 and split chords) / 2 versions in different keys / suggestions for special voicings.
Arranged to play as a reggae tune using minor and minor 7th chords.
